fields.series_labels: Total | < 150 cm | Prev C-Sect | Prev Death | Prev Bleed | Heart Probs | Diabetes | Hip Probs | Syphilis | Hep B | Long Time | Low Hemoglb | Rare Blood
fields.db_query:
select 
count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'no')) as high_risk,
count(nullif(sampledata_mother_height,'over_150')) as small_frame,
count(nullif(sampledata_previous_csection,'no')) as previous_c_section,
count(nullif(sampledata_previous_newborn_death,'no')) as previous_newborn_death,
count(nullif(sampledata_previous_bleeding,'no')) as previous_bleeding,
count(nullif(sampledata_heart_problems,'no')) as heart_problems,
count(nullif(sampledata_diabetes,'no')) as diabetes,
count(nullif(sampledata_hip_problems,'no')) as hip_problems,
count(nullif(sampledata_card_results_syphilis_result,'negative')) as syphilis,
count(nullif(sampledata_card_results_hepb_result,'negative')) as hebp,
count(nullif(sampledata_over_5_years,'no')) as time_since_last,
count(nullif(sampledata_card_results_hb_test,'normal')) as low_hemoglobin,
count(nullif(sampledata_card_results_blood_group, 'opositive') OR
         nullif(sampledata_card_results_blood_group, 'apositive') OR
         nullif(sampledata_card_results_blood_group, 'abpositive') OR
         nullif(sampledata_card_results_blood_group, 'bpositive')) as rare_blood


from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3

where meta_username <> 'admin';

fields.y_axis_label: Percent of Registrations which are High Risk
fields.db_query:
select DATE_FORMAT(a.meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'),
(
(100 * (select count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'no')) from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3 where meta_timeend <=a.meta_timeend)) /
(select count(sampledata_hi_risk) from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3 where meta_timeend <=a.meta_timeend)) as percent_hi_risk

from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3 as a

where a.meta_username <> 'admin'

group by DATE_FORMAT(a.meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y');

select   DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'),
((100 * count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'no'))) / count(sampledata_hi_risk)) as hi_risk

from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3  

where meta_username <> 'admin'

group by DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y');

select   DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'),
count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'no')) as hi_risk, 
count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'yes')) as low_risk 

from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3  

group by DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y');

select   DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'),
count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'no')) as hi_risk, 
count(nullif(sampledata_hi_risk,'yes')) as low_risk 

from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_3  

group by DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y');

select  DATE_FORMAT(timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'), username, count(*)
from xformmanager_metadata meta,
xformmanager_formdefmodel forms, hq_domain domains
where forms.id = meta.formdefmodel_id
and forms.domain_id = domains.id
and domains.name = '{{domain}}'
and meta.timeend > '{{startdate}}'
and meta.timeend < '{{enddate}}'
group by
DATE_FORMAT(timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'), username
order by timeend asc;

select meta.username, count(*) as cnt from xformmanager_metadata meta,
xformmanager_formdefmodel forms, hq_domain domains
where forms.id = meta.formdefmodel_id
and forms.domain_id = domains.id
and domains.name = '{{domain}}'
group by username

select meta.username, count(*) as cnt from xformmanager_metadata meta,
xformmanager_formdefmodel forms, hq_domain domains
where forms.id = meta.formdefmodel_id
and forms.domain_id = domains.id
and domains.name = '{{domain}}'
and meta.timeend > '{{startdate}}'
and meta.timeend < '{{enddate}}'
group by username

select 
distinct(meta_username), 
avg(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(meta_timeend) - UNIX_TIMESTAMP(meta_timestart)) as avg 
from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_2
group by meta_username

select
 distinct(sampledata_previous_pregnancies), 
 count(*) 
from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_2

where sampledata_previous_pregnancies between '0' and '10'

group by sampledata_previous_pregnancies 

ORDER BY sampledata_previous_pregnancies ASC

select 
 DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'),
 avg(sampledata_previous_pregnancies) as avgbirth

from schema_intel_grameen_safe_motherhood_registration_v0_2

group by
DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y')
;

fields.series_labels: TB Test|Malaria|Preg Mother|Ante Natal|HIV Test|Birth Registration
fields.db_query:
select
  DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y'), 
  sum(brac_referral_given_tb_test),
  sum(brac_referral_given_malaria),
  sum(brac_referral_given_preg_mother_tt),
  sum(brac_referral_given_preg_mother_ante_natal),
  sum(brac_referral_given_hiv_test),
  sum(brac_referral_given_birth_registration)
from schema_brac_chp_homevisit_v0_0_1
where 
brac_referral = 'y'
group by
DATE_FORMAT(meta_timeend,'%%m/%%d/%%Y')
order by meta_timeend asc;
